author: IMRAN GHORI
title: MORENO VALLEY: Volunteers sought
text:
By IMRAN GHORI / STAFF WRITER
Published: Oct. 9, 2015 2:59 p.m. MORENO VALLEY: Volunteers sought Print Photo Share Pin It More Galleries ADVERTISEMENT Moreno Valley is seeking volunteers. , DAVID BAUMAN, FILE PHOTO Related article » Moreno Valley is looking for volunteers to join its “Keep Moreno Valley Beautiful” program.
Volunteers will assist property-owners in correcting code enforcement violations and be involved in neighborhood litter clean-ups.
For more information, contact Julie Reyes at (951) 413-3047 or MoValRecycles@moval.org .
